      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "Boise, Idaho",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Dear Mr. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Quite obviously you have been ribbed so much you'd like to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "forget the flying saucers--but I'd sure like to have your",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "personal story, your photo, pic of your plane, etc. as I",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "asked before. And you won't be made to look silly, because",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "there's more to this than the newspapers and the \"experts\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "have made of it.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "Besides the article, I have another proposition. You seem to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "get around quite a bit, and if you can make a trip to Tacoma,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "Washington at all feasible, I'd be willing to pay expenses",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "plus a nice amount to make it worth your while.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "I'd want you to see [REDACTED], Fern",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "Hill Station, Tacoma, and [REDACTED], owner of the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "[REDACTED] and two other seamen, on a",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "patrol near Murry Island, off Tacoma, saw six discs, one in",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "trouble, witnessed an explosion, saw falling stuff which",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "smashed their wheelhouse and searchlight and landed on the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "beach. They sent me samples which Chicago U has failed to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "analyze. I want a picture of the beach and the stuff that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "landed there (about twenty tons, they said). And I want",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "somebody who'll get the truth, to find out if these boys are",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "on the up and up. You could do that. I hope you will. If",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "agreeable, please write and perhaps we can talk business.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "I think you'd like to prove this thing too!",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "Anyway, I still want that article!",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
